# Persistent Sales Assistant Agent

A FastAPI-based AI Sales Assistant that provides product information, maintains persistent cross-session memory, uses real tools for retrieval, and generates a self-evaluation score for every response.

## Features

* Persistent user memory stored in SQLite
* Product catalog search tool
* User memory retrieval tool
* Response self-evaluation (groundedness, relevance, confidence)
* Session tracking with UUIDs
* Conversation history retrieval
* Memory deletion (GDPR-style reset)
* Eval analytics endpoint
* FastAPI Swagger documentation

---

# Architecture

```text
                 +------------------+
                 |     Client       |
                 +--------+---------+
                          |
                          v
                POST /chat/{user_id}
                          |
                          v
                +------------------+
                |   FastAPI API    |
                +--------+---------+
                         |
                         v
                +------------------+
                |   Chat Agent     |
                +--------+---------+
                         |
        +----------------+----------------+
        |                                 |
        v                                 v
+----------------+             +------------------+
| search_catalog |             | get_user_memory  |
+----------------+             +------------------+
        |                                 |
        +---------------+-----------------+
                        |
                        v
               Generate Response
                        |
                        v
               Evaluate Response
                        |
                        v
                Return JSON Output
                        |
                        v
                  Store in SQLite
```

